org.daisy.pipeline.client.models

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.pipeline.client.models.Client

  • public class Client
extends Object
    A representation of the "/admin/clients" response from the Pipeline 2 Web Service. GET /admin/clients <clients href="http://localhost:8181/ws/admin/clients" xmlns="http://www.daisy.org/ns/pipeline/data"> <client id="" href="" secret="" role="" contact=""/> </clients> GET /admin/clients/{clientId}
